data.description: Amazing Views! Moonridge area with in walking distance to Bear Mountain, Big Bear Golf course , Alpine zoo. Great updated deck for entertaining enjoying the sunset or sunrise. This home is 3 levels with 2 upstairs and a large bedroom downstairs with access to the backyard large enough to add another deck and a spa. Living room on the main level has a beautiful fire place with a view of surrounding trees. You do not want to miss out on this great home
